### ===== LISTAS =====

### Obtener todas las listas de un tablón
GET http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear una nueva lista
POST http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Por Hacer",
  "color": "#ff6b6b"
}

### ===== TAREAS =====

### Obtener todas las tareas de una lista
GET http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists/{{listId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear una nueva tarea
POST http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists/{{listId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Primera Tarea"
}

### Eliminar una tarea
DELETE http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists/{{listId}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar una lista
DELETE http://localhost:3000/boards/{{boardId}}/lists/{{listId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
